Subject: [PATCH v7 3/4] PCI: brcmstb: Wait for Raspberry Pi's firmware when present
Date:   Wed, 29 Apr 2020 18:47:33 +0200
Message-Id: <20200429164734.21506-4-nsaenzjulienne@suse.de>
